{"tid":653052,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解依家D男人咁小器！？","createTime":"2018-05-04T10:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T11:45:21.000Z","uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"038ffc31eca20c3d745e194f7d8c63d985e4b307","tid":653052,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:57:00.000Z","msg":"件事就係咁嘅，我男朋友本身有鼻敏感，<br />\n之前同佢訓間唔中都會比佢D鼻鼾聲嘈醒，<br />\n但呢排唔知係咪天氣原因啦，佢鼻敏感都幾嚴重，<br />\n成個禮拜都比佢D嘈到鼻鼾聲嘈到冇覺好訓，<br />\n其實我都知佢唔想咁，但忍咗咁耐我個人都好躁，<br />\n前晚同佢食飯個陣就忍唔住話咗佢兩句，開玩笑咁叫佢去訓梳化<br />\n點知佢聽完竟然就黑曬面咁，成晚都唔同我講嘢<br />\n我都唔明點解佢可以小器成咁，開兩句玩笑竟然嬲我嬲到依家！"},{"pid":"18959fd1274613024d0ff8579a68c0e82c3fd496","tid":653052,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:58:14.000Z","msg":"戴耳塞訓 o 唔ok?<br />\n佢都唔想嘈到你就咪笑鳩人喇"},{"pid":"8eda9de23d98427d563b62fc239665db3ed4d859","tid":653052,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"sorry ar"},{"pid":"f18ae69adff20d9a8f6a9ec6d4685583464fab7e","tid":653052,"uid":170867,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"兩個男人就成熟d啦屌"},{"pid":"2b2ffe2f9cb488648338914840ffa94684ab0750","tid":653052,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會係覺得你嫌棄佢<br />\n鼻敏感其實都幾辛苦 你有冇關心過<br />\n換著係你又點 <br />\nBb我冇嬲你啦"},{"pid":"575e86ec13e5e2aa8524d3a895408029a7b527e0","tid":653052,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNI7pip.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJNI7pip.gif&h=21722eb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"120073aaa4883beed1db194e3272432bbe8c6657","tid":653052,"uid":21355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"575e86ec13e5e2aa8524d3a895408029a7b527e0","tid":653052,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: